rt developing new components: </span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #2f2f2f; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">com_config</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #2f2f2f; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">, </span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #2f2f2f; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">com_plugins</span></p>', NULL, 1, 760, 4, 4420, '2019-05-27 22:00:00', 4420, '2019-08-24 09:31:19', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1075, 0, 153, 'Joomla GSoC 2019 Webservices - June 10, 2019', 'fourths-meeting-joomla-gsoc-2019-webservices', '<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.656; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 7pt 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Date: 10th Jun 2019</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.656; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 7pt 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Time: 22:00 (GMT+3)</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.656; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 7pt 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Meeting was attended by: George Wilson, Andrei Isac, Oleksandr Samoilov</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.656; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 7pt 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Meeting venue: Hangouts</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.656; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 7pt 0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.999999