>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: circle; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Helpdesk form to be reviewed to add Virtual location</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: circle; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Magazine Article</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: circle; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Laura agreed to put together a detailed list and then we contact the appropriate persons</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Meeting closed: 21:03UTC</span></p>', NULL, 1, 1148, 6, 901, '2021-03-08 07:33:52', 901, '2021-06-23 09:21:57', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1463, 56, 0, 'Programs Department Meeting - 2nd March 2021', 'programs-department-meeting-2nd-march-2021', '<p id="docs-internal-guid-290832ec-7fff-8fa7-0ba3-5645936b05b2" dir="ltr">Participants: Jaz Parkyn, Chris Keen, Patrick Jackson, Wilco Alsemgeest, Todd Woodward,&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Apologies: Shirielle Williams</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Minutes:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Dept&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Jaz informed Todd that the board has written a response to the Educational Outreach Working Group’s questions and that the document has been emailed across to them.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Jaz thanked everyone for getting the agenda populated ahead of the meeting time.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">JCP&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Andrea has decided to step down from the team, everyone thanks her for all of her time and hard work.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Chris shared some updates about the team’s planning for the new exam and continued testing of the new exam component.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">The department members discussed the best location for managing the questions, so that only team members have access. Wilco suggested to use the QMS that was previously created for this purpose.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Three volunteers have stepped forward who are willing to help review and update the exam question sets.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">VET&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Patrick explained that the team is continuing to work on defining their mission and goals statements, as well as the onboarding document.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Significant progress has been made in February on both Help Wanted and Onboarding projects, and during March the team will be reaching out to other teams (Webmasters and JVP) to start discussing access to update various information and features on the various sites.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">JEO</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Todd thanked Jaz for the answers to the questions that the team raised with the board, and reiterated their concerns. Jaz suggested that the team review the response and then revert with any further concerns. Jaz will attend the team’s next meeting to aid this process.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Other business</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir="ltr" aria-level="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Jaz and Wilco informed the department members of the passed board motion that means that the Programs Department will shortly welcome a new team - Joomla Translation Program (JTP) Team. The team is a combination of the two previously separate translation teams from the Production and Marketing Departments.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 1, 1149, 1, 695, '2021-03-10 12:18:45', 0, '2021-03-10 12:19:19', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1464, 0, 44, 'JED Team Meeting - March 5th, 2021 ', 'jed-team-meeting-march-5th-2021', '<h1 style="text-align: right;">Joomla Extension Directory. Meeting Minutes <br />- March 5, 2021</h1>\r\n<p><strong>Participants:</strong> Anibal Sanchez, Jaz Parkyn (Assistant Team Lead), Mark Lee, Llewellyn van der Merwe (Team Lead), Wilco Alsemgeest (Department Coordinator), Hugh Douglas-Smith<br /> <strong>Absent with notice: </strong>Claire Mandville<br /> <strong>Absent without notice:</strong> Dénes Székely, Luca Marzo, Tobias Zulauf (JSST Liaison)</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Team Organization:</strong> Llewellyn van der Merwe, Jaz Parkyn</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Increase usage of JED Github project management tools to better organize the team’s ongoing and outstanding tasks.</li>\r\n<li>Please continue to add details of historic investigation cases / bans, repeat offenders, big issues etc to our internal central team records on Drive.</li>\r\n<li>We need to write a notice to confront any contradiction on the licensing submitted to the JED, and the consequences if a violation is detected.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><strong>Tickets:</strong> Dénes Székely, Mark Lee</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Abandonware - how to handle it.\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>A recent ticket reminded us all that the report path is not that clear in regards to abandonware, and we need some improvement, both as internal rules/procedures, and public communication.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><strong>JED Extensions:</strong> Llewellyn van der Merwe, Jaz Parkyn</h3>\r\n<h4>JED Extension Checker [J3]</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>We need more collaboration from the team on the GitHub repo to best investigate contributions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><strong>JED Website:</strong> Jaz Parkyn</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The cleantalk and hcaptcha integration is still on going.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><strong>JED 4:</strong> Jaz Parkyn</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Christopher Wagner has joined the JED4 discussions to help advise on SEO matters.</li>\r\n<li>Roland is updating the repo to run on Joomla 4</li>\r\n<li>Mark has been analyzing the database structures in preparation for the eventual migration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><strong>Social &amp; Forums:</strong> Dénes Székely, Anibal Sanchez</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Motion: Removal of the Joomla Extension Directory social media accounts on Facebook and Twitter.<br /> Proposed by Jaz Parkyn, seconded by Llewellyn van der Merwe <br /><strong>Motion passed unanimously</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>Other Business</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>TL proposes to adjourn the Meeting</strong><br /> Proposed by Llewellyn van der Merwe seconded by Jaz Parkyn</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 1, 1150, 2, 1755, '2021-03-12 21:26:23', 1755, '2021-05-20 11:10:42', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1465, 0, 25, 'Joomla Bug Squad Team Meeting - March 12, 2021', 'joomla-bug-squad-team-meeting-march-12-2021', '<p id="docs-internal-guid-84c07486-7fff-2afe-89ab-c6712650d8ee" dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Date:</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> March 12, 2021</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Time:</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> 19:10 CET</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Total time of meeting:</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> 45 minutes</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Attendees:</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Richard Fath, Nicola Galgano, Christiane Maier-Stadtherr, Jacob Waisner, Luca Racchetti, Sandra Decoux</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Discussion outline</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">During this meeting we discussed the following topics:</span></p>\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Current Status</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Team Leader Election Results</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Thank you Nicola!</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Current Status</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Release blockers were the topic of focus for J4. We have 18 open RBs with 7 of those having PRs. We discussed reviewing those and determining next steps with the release lead on what can be moved to 4.1.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">If anyone would like to contribute to the Release blockers or with the Project as a whole please join us on GitHub at </span><a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms" style="text-decoration: none;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #1155cc; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms</span></a><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> .</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Team Leader Election Results</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Election results below:</span></p>\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Nicola: 4 votes</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Jacob: 4 votes</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Abstain: 2</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Didn\'t vote: 2</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">After discussing in the Team meeting the original plan was to run another election, however, Nicola respectively abdicated to Jacob.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Congratulations to Jacob Waisner!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Thank you Nicola!</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The team wants to extend an ENORMOUS thank you to Nicola for his leadership over his time as Team Leader and the impact he had on the team to revamp the JBS and invite new members to this team. He will remain a member of JBS and we look forward to squashing many more bugs with him.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Next Meeting</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The next team meeting will be: Fri, 26 March at 7:00 PM CEST</span></p>', NULL, 1, 1151, 1, 1053, '2021-03-14 17:27:59', 0, '2021-03-14 17:29:51', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1466, 0, 32, 'JSST Team Leader Election results (2021)', 'jsst-team-leader-election-results-2021', '<p><strong>Team Leader Election Results</strong></p>\r\n<p>Election results below:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>David Jardin: 7 votes</li>\r\n<li>None of the above: 0</li>\r\n<li>Abstain: 1</li>\r\n<li>Didn\'t vote: 2</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The vote has been held between the 05.03. and 12.03.2021 by the 10 members of the team.</p>\r\n<p>David Jardin accepted the voting and is thereby is the current and new team leader for the JSST.</p>', NULL, 1, 1152, 1, 601, '2021-03-14 20:02:26', 0, '2021-03-14 20:12:21', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1467, 0, 51, 'CMS Release Team Meeting March 17, 2021', 'cms-release-team-meeting-march-17-2021', '<p><span id="docs-internal-guid-c428a97b-7fff-54aa-0764-7b8def0c3535" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Wed, March 17, 2021, UTC 18:00</span></p>\r\n<p id="docs-internal-guid-88ed4031-7fff-c546-a73f-372965fabc5d" dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 14pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">DETAILS</span><span style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br /></span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Duration: 60 min</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 14pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Participants:</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Sigrid Gramlinger (Team Leader), Jenn Gress, Philip Walton, Rachel Walraven, Tobias Zulauf (3.10 Release Lead)</span></p>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 14pt; margin-bottom: 4pt;"><span style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">AGENDA</span></h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">1. </span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #282b33; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Joomla 4.0</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">George has asked for testing of the following issues. We shortly talked about them, what and how to test.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">[4.0] Migrate data for repeatable fields</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br /></span><a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/32611" style="text-decoration: none;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #2559e4; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/32611</span></a><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">[4.0] Re-Implementing FTP-layer during CMS installation</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br /></span><a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/31857" style="text-decoration: none;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #2559e4; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/31857</span></a></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">2. Joomla 3.10</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Tobias asked for testing the Pre-Upgrade Compatibility Check on complex environments.</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br /></span><a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/31200" style="text-decoration: none;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #1155cc; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/31200</span></a></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">3. </span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #282b33; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">EOS Plugin</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #282b33; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Jenn and Rachel had provided us with two versions of suggestions for the plugin messages. We discussed the balance of Marketing and technical messages.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Rachel will work on the next draft of messages this week. We will have about 6 returning messages for the first weeks. We will have links to marketing articles and to the pre-update check, as well as to the documentation about planning and processing a migration.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Philip and Tobias will publish the plugin without a date for the release. For testing purposes, there is a date field in the plugin options to simulate different weeks/stages of support time. This field will be removed before final merging.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">4. Testing check component</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Sigrid gave some information about the current status of the com_release_checking component. There needs to be some more concept and we might wait for Joomla 4 to have the component there. Then we will proceed with more functionality.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>Next meeting scheduled for Wed April, 14th 18:00 UTC. (beware of Daylight Saving changes!)</strong></p>', NULL, 1, 1153, 1, 1036, '2021-03-20 15:30:23', 0, '2021-03-20 15:32:19', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1468, 0, 78, 'Certification Program: team meeting - March 17th, 2021', 'certification-program-team-meeting-march-17th-2021', '<p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;">The JCP March monthly team meeting was held on March 17th, 2021 at 18:00 (UTC) using Google Meet.</p>\r\n<h3 style="font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333;">Participants:</h3>\r\n<p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"><em>Attendees:</em><span style="caret-color: auto;"></span><span style="caret-color: auto;">Chris Keen (TL),&nbsp;</span><span style="caret-color: auto;">Jeroen Moolenschot</span></p>\r\n<p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"><em>Absent with apologies:&nbsp;</em><span style="caret-color: auto;">Luca Marzo, Andrea Gentil (ATL)<br /><em>Guest:</em>&nbsp;Jaz Parkyn (Dept. Co-ordinator) - not present<br /></span></p>\r\n<h2 style="font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333;">General points</h2>\r\n<p><span id="docs-internal-guid-db13cfb0-7fff-1e7f-2d9c-50751520fef3">The team discussed the following topics (documents / proposals)<br /></span></p>\r\n<h3 style="font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-db13cfb0-7fff-1e7f-2d9c-50751520fef3">Team news</span></h3>\r\n<p><span id="docs-internal-guid-db13cfb0-7fff-1e7f-2d9c-50751520fef3">Andrea Gentil has decided to withdraw from the JCP due to personal reasons. Andrea has been a member of the JCP team since 2016 and has been Assistant Team Leader for the last two years, and was responsible for coordinating the Operations and Marketing tasks and processes.<br />We would like to thank Andrea for all her time and work for the JCP and the community over the last few years.<br /><br />We are now working with Andrea to ensure a full handover of tasks and processes. Once this has been completed we will then begin recruiting new members for the JCP to fulfil this role.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style="overflow-wrap: break-word;">Operations and Marketing</h2>\r\n<p><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: auto;"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px;">There are no updates from the Operations and Marketint team (mainly due to the lack of exams).</span><span style="font-size: 14.6667px;"><br />We have now published a blog post \'<a href="https://certification.joomla.org/news/205-the-covid-19-pandemic-and-its-effect-on-the-joomla-certification-program" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The COVID-19 pandemic and its effect on the Joomla Certification Program</a>\' </span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: auto;"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px;">on the Certification site. This post explains the current situation regarding certification exams. We have also posted a second blog expalining why we do not offer \'online\' exams \'<a href="https://certification.joomla.org/news/206-online-exams-why-does-joomla-not-offer-online-exams" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Online exams - why does Joomla not offer online exams?</a>. </span></span></p>\r\n<h2><span id="docs-internal-guid-db13cfb0-7fff-1e7f-2d9c-50751520fef3">Website and Exam platform</span></h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Shika: (new exam platform):</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Jeroen has been testing the new exam platform according to the test plan. Any issues are being discussed and tackled when found. At this point in time&nbsp; we have not found any \'show stoppers\' and hopefully will be able to implement and be able to use the platform by the end of May 2021.</p>\r\n<h2 style="font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-db13cfb0-7fff-1e7f-2d9c-50751520fef3">Exam(s)</span></h2>\r\n<h3 style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: auto;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-db13cfb0-7fff-1e7f-2d9c-50751520fef3" style="color: #333333; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span></span></span>J!3 exam update</h3>\r\n<p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: auto;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-fa6f5df6-7fff-6772-8e79-e390e9ee64f5" style="color: #333333; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><em>We are now preparing to update the J!3 Adminstrator exam to Joomla v 3.10</em>. <em style="font-size: 14.6667px;">By doing this, firstly, we can still support candidates who went to certify for J!3, which will still be supported for two years. Secondly the updated J!3 exam will be used as the base for the J!4 version of the exam. Thirdly, we can use the updated J!3 exam to \'test\' the new exam platform (Shika) in preparation for offering the J!4 version, and eventually other exams.</em><br />We are currently working on a \'system\' to be able to review and update any outdated Questions and Answers (Q&amp;A\'s) and add new Q&amp;A\'s for new functionality.<br />We have also recruited two Exam Maintainers who will help us update the J!3 version of the exam and then work on the J!4 version.<br /> <br /><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Meeting(s):</span><br /></span></span></span>Next:<strong>&nbsp;Project / isssue progress meeting:&nbsp;</strong>Wednesday March 24th, 2021 at 18:00 UTC&nbsp;<br /><br />Next:<strong>&nbsp;JCP monthly team meeting:&nbsp;</strong>Wednesday April 14th, 2021 at 18:00 UTC&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 1, 1154, 6, 1093, '2021-03-22 18:07:24', 1093, '2021-03-22 19:22:57', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1469, 0, 150, 'Joomla Educational Outreach Working Group Meeting - March 19, 2021', 'wg-3-2021', '<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">In Attendance: </span><a href="mailto:laura.gordon@community.joomla.org" style="text-decoration: none;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #1155cc; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Laura Gordon</span></a><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">, </span><a href="mailto:toddw@creativepeopleconsulting.com" style="text-decoration: none;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #1155cc; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Todd Woodward</span></a><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">, Jaz Parkyn, Abdulkadir Shehu, Shirelle “SD” Williams, Marco Dings, Wilco Alsemgeest</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Regrets: </span><a href="mailto:chris.keen@community.joomla.org" style="text-decoration: none;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #1155cc; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Chris Keen</span></a></p>\r\n<h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Agenda Items</span></h2>\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Chris: Trademark Update</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Items tabled until this meeting:</span></p>\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: circle; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Team: Submission, standards, and vetting process</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: circle; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Team: Brainstorm content structure and categories</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: circle; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-heigh