="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br /></span><a style="text-decoration: none;" href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YobrMd-zhOFXV1e45JSB-dzCBaJdNywgOPLBCcsZ-1o/edit#heading=h.1hpjmp5admdu"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Beta blocker discussion document</span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br /></span></a><a style="text-decoration: none;" href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1A6-gT1fG00aKM9Czv_f393cK9Qmnc5GMW9UjFJVBXNo/edit#gid=0"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Blocker estimates spreadsheet</span></a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Updates/Proposed Topics:</span></p>\r\n<ol style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;" start="2">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Status of UX has not been addressed&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Marianela brought up the idea of putting a form to get insightful data</span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br /></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">(Type of website: e-commerce, educational website, information website, etc.. experience of the user/admin with joomla: ie: new, amateur, experienced, and last if the user is: free lance web developer, agency, or company). This will help marketing efforts and possibly the future of the product</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">RFC discussion for technical questions and features initially and then see if it can be implemented for productions</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Help for Joomla 4 for BETA version. BETA blockers were identified. Llewellyn volunteered to help with the estimates, and Marco will try to find a way to inform the community, Marianela will bring it to marketing to put in a blog post.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Team leader: Niels Braczek. Assistant team leader: Marco Dings</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><br /><br /><br /><br /></p>', NULL, 1, 898, 2, 597, '2020-03-10 08:41:37', 597, '2020-04-06 10:43:58', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1213, 51, 0, 'Production Dept. Meeting - March 24, 2020 ', 'production-dept-meeting-march-24-2020', '<h2 id="docs-internal-guid-a9a076e5-7fff-76ef-f16e-bc858063deda" dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Production Department Meeting Agenda March 24, 2020 at 18:00:00&nbsp; UTC&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Participants:</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> Marco Dings (Department Coordinator), Harald Leithner (Release Lead),&nbsp; Philip Walton (Team Leader), Benjamin Trenkle (Team Leader), Hannes Papenberg (Team Leader), Robert Deutz (Team Leader), Nicola Galgano (Team Leader), Niels Braczek (Team Leader), Tobias Zulauf (Release Lead), George Wilson (Release Lead)</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Apologies: </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;David Jardin (Team Leader), Carlos Cámara (Team Leader), Mike Brandner (Team Leader), Ilagnayeru Manickam (Team Leader), Puneet Kala (Team Leader)</span></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 14pt; margin-bottom: 4pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Agenda Items &amp; minutes:</span></h3>\r\n<div dir="ltr" style="margin-left: -5pt;" align="left">\r\n<table style="border: none; border-collapse: collapse;"><colgroup><col width="467" /><col width="149" /></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style="height: 0pt;">\r\n<td style="vertical-align: top; background-color: #efefef; padding: 5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: solid #000000 0.5pt;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Report from the Department Coordinator</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="vertical-align: top; background-color: #efefef; padding: 5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: solid #000000 0.5pt;">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="height: 102pt;">\r\n<td style="vertical-align: top; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: solid #000000 0.5pt;" colspan="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Talk Topics:</span></p>\r\n<ol style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">There was no board meeting since last last PD meeting</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Tobias is added as release lead</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Niels is added as TL for SA&amp;S</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Wilco claims to be able to scrape joomlacode. What were the reasons this failed in the past. Please add encountered problems here. Wilco will document his findings</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">PDC in process of obtaining privileges, with this cycle we will move to role based access</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div dir="ltr" style="margin-left: -5pt;" align="left">\r\n<table style="border: none; border-collapse: collapse;"><colgroup><col width="467" /><col width="149" /></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style="height: 0pt;">\r\n<td style="vertical-align: top; background-color: #efefef; padding: 5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: solid #000000 0.5pt;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Release Leads</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="vertical-align: top; background-color: #efefef; padding: 5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: solid #000000 0.5pt;">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="height: 22pt;">\r\n<td style="vertical-align: top; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: solid #000000 0.5pt;" colspan="2">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Joomla 3 Release Lead:</span></p>\r\n<ol style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">There is an issue with time fields on article reloads ( </span><a style="text-decoration: none;" href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/issues/28386"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #1155cc; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/issues/28386</span></a><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> ) that have to be fixed, as soon as we have a fix I will shorten the release cycle to 4 weeks, if we don’t get a fix I will revert the problematic pull request.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Joomla 4 Release Lead:</span></p>\r\n<ol style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Expect remaining hard beta blockers will be solved by the end of this week</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Thanks to Richard F for his hard work on fixing the 3.10 to 4.0 update stream</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Continued writing the documentation page of j4 b/c breaks</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div dir="ltr" style="margin-left: -5pt;" align="left">\r\n<table style="border: none; border-collapse: collapse;"><colgroup><col width="467" /><col width="149" /></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style="height: 0pt;">\r\n<td style="ver