normal;"><span style="color: #333333;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>Data Cleansing</b></span></span></span></span><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal;"><span style="color: #333333;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">, we are preparing a cleanup of old reviews and the anonymization of old accounts without activity.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p class="western" style="margin-bottom: 0in; direction: ltr; line-height: 29.6px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Liberation Serif\', serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal;"><span style="color: #333333;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>Call for JED4 Developers</b></span></span></span></span><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal;"><span style="color: #333333;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">. We have submitted a position for the community openings JCM article to call for JED4 Developers. To contribute to the project, </span></span></span></span><a href="https://github.com/joomla/com_jed4/" class="western" style="color: #000080; text-decoration-line: underline;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal;"><span style="color: #0088cc;"><span style="text-decoration-line: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span lang="zxx">join the team!</span></span></span></span></span></span></a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p class="western" style="margin-bottom: 0in; direction: ltr; line-height: 29.6px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Liberation Serif\', serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal;"><span style="color: #333333;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">We are processing the queue of new extensions and pending tickets within the seven days processing window. With the addition of new members, we are improving the processing times.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p class="western" style="margin-bottom: 0.17in; direction: ltr; line-height: 29.6px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Liberation Serif\', serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal;"><span style="color: #333333;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>JED LinkChecker </b></span></span></span></span><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal;"><span style="color: #333333;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">is fully operational, processing 10% of the extensions per day.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 class="western" style="margin-top: 0.25in; margin-bottom: 0.06in; direction: ltr; color: #000000; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; break-after: avoid; font-family: \'Liberation Sans\', serif; font-size: 18pt; margin-left: 0.26in; line-height: 40.08px;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal;"><span style="color: #333333;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: 17pt;">Plans</span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<ul style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class="western" style="margin-bottom: 0in; direction: ltr; line-height: 29.6px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Liberation Serif\', serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal;"><span style="color: #333333;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>Spam Checks for Reviews - IP Detective Deprecation: </b></span></span></span></span><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal;"><span style="color: #333333;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">New method of review validations based on hCaptcha and CleanTalk / November.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p class="western" style="margin-bottom: 0in; direction: ltr; line-height: 21.92px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Liberation Serif\', serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal;"><span style="color: #333333;"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">The current system to process Spam Review needs to be revamped. The current implementation has several shortcomings that must be addressed.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p class="western" style="margin-bottom: 0in; direction: ltr; line-height: 21.92px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; backgr