-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">OSM domain name servers has been switched to CloudFlare (a week ago), as this was successful the joomla.org domain was also done on November 15th, 2020</span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Roboto,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span></li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 1, 1061, 2, 2198, '2020-11-19 14:35:53', 2198, '2020-11-19 14:42:13', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
